---
---

<section class="bg-surface-container-low py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
    <div class="text-center mb-12 space-y-3">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold text-primary">Cómo funciona</h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body max-w-lg mx-auto">
        Tres pasos simples para descubrir tu afinidad electoral.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <article class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center text-on-secondary-container">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">edit_note</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-primary mb-2">Paso 1</p>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-extrabold text-primary mb-3">Responde</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            Marca tu postura en ocho temas clave del debate público peruano.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center text-on-secondary-container">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">compare_arrows</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-primary mb-2">Paso 2</p>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-extrabold text-primary mb-3">Compara</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            Revisa el ranking de afinidad y en qué ejes coincide más cada candidatura contigo.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center text-on-secondary-container">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">search</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-primary mb-2">Paso 3</p>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-extrabold text-primary mb-3">Profundiza</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            Usa el resultado como punto de partida y luego contrástalo con fuentes oficiales.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
